OL,3,CBritish Army pays tribute to soldier
OL,4,Cafter death in 'non-operational
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,FA solider has died in what the
OL,8,FMinistry of Defence has described as a
OL,9,F'non-operational incident' in Brecon.
OL,11,FThe MoD has confirmed Corporal (Cpl)
OL,12,FChristopher Gill, who served in the
OL,13,F4th Battalion, The Ranger Regiment,
OL,14,Fdied on Wednesday (16 October).
OL,16,FCpl Gill's professional life saw him
OL,17,Fdeployed in Afghanistan and sped time
OL,18,Fin Belize, the US, Kenya and Morocco
OL,19,Fas well as training Ukrainian soldiers
OL,20,Fin the UK.
