OL,3,CBritish Army pays tribute to soldier
OL,4,Cafter death in 'non-operational
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,F"Dedicated to his family, Cpl Gill's
OL,8,Fprofessionalism and commitment to
OL,9,Fservice inspired those around him and
OL,10,Fleft him held in the highest regard
OL,11,Facross RIFLES, RANGER and Army Special
OL,12,FOperations communities. He excelled
OL,13,Fthroughout his thirteen years'
OL,14,Fservice. A chosen man who will be
OL,15,Fsorely missed.
