OL,3,CBritish Army pays tribute to soldier
OL,4,Cafter death in 'non-operational
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,F"Joining the British Army in 2011, Cpl
OL,8,FGill initially served in 4th
OL,9,FBattalion, The Rifles. From the start
OL,10,Fhis initiative, soldiering skill and
OL,11,Fhonest manner highlighted him as a
OL,12,Ffuture leader. He flourished,
OL,13,Fdeploying to Helmand Province on Op
OL,14,FHERRICK 18, bravely contributing to
OL,15,Fthe security of the local population
OL,16,Fon a tough, hard-fought tour.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/9
