OL,3,CBritish Army pays tribute to soldier
OL,4,Cafter death in 'non-operational
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,F"Daring to do more, in 2021 Cpl Gill
OL,8,Fvolunteered for Army Special
OL,9,FOperations. Passing the assessment, he
OL,10,Fjoined 4th Battalion, The Ranger
OL,11,FRegiment where his talents and
OL,12,Fdedication made an enormous
OL,13,Fdifference. Training and operating
OL,14,Foverseas, his contributions set
OL,15,Fcrucial foundations for the
OL,16,Fdevelopment of the Battalion's
OL,17,Fcapabilities and culture.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
