OL,3,CBritish Army pays tribute to soldier
OL,4,Cafter death in 'non-operational
OL,5,Cincident'
OL,7,F"Selfless and dedicated, Cpl Gill was
OL,8,Fquick to volunteer to train Ukrainian
OL,9,Fsoldiers in the UK, testament to his
OL,10,Fcommitment to service and preservation
OL,11,Fof our freedoms. A highly regarded
OL,12,Fmember of Team 9, he was a brilliant
OL,13,Fmentor in R Company and a charismatic
OL,14,Fpresence loved in the Battalion.
OL,16,F"He always took the time to develop
OL,17,Fnewer Rangers and as a straight talker
OL,18,Fdemanded the highest standards,
OL,19,Fwinning the respect and admiration
OL,20,Facross the Battalion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/9
